      <title>
        <text font="bold">4.3 Corollary.</text>
      </title>
      <p>
        <text font="italic">Admitting reflection and rotation, a three-legged pig <Math mode="inline" tex="P" text="P"><XMath><XMTok role="UNKNOWN">P</XMTok></XMath></Math> is capable of
standing on the corners of a triangle <Math mode="inline" tex="T" text="T"><XMath><XMTok role="UNKNOWN">T</XMTok></XMath></Math> iff (<ref labelref="sdqsw"/>) holds.
